Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:36.00,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be1\an8}翻译：味精；校对：七海·拓；歌词听写：ever silver；\N特效：Noeru、Tiger Soldier；时间：夜、后期：zipwinmax；繁化：黑羽侖人。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:10.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}さらば　昨日までの口づけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:14.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}さらば　いとおしき胸の痛みよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}まあ　それはそれとしてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:20.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}何とか今日も生きています
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}孤独とか過去とか噂とか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:30.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}欲望とか身内とかクセとか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}明日からおれらきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.62,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もう笑われずにすみそうだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:41.53,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}“信じていればいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:44.51,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}気持ちはちゃんと伝わってくよ…”と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:50.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ふざけないでよ　だって　そうじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もう　どこへも逃げたりしたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:59.48,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}誰が“yes！”といって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}だって　昨日の場所には戻れない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:07.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君といた場所には
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:11.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もう　誰にも言い訳したくない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:16.01,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}だから“yes！”といって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:20.03,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}だって誰でもいーわけない　そうじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:24.47,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君じゃなきゃ意味がない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:29.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}こたえなんか　誰も知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:10.00,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}再见了  终结于昨日的亲吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:14.35,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}再见了  我那可怜的心伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.68,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}算了  不提也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:20.11,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今天也先想方设法活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.79,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}什么孤独  过去  和传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:30.88,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}什么欲望  全身  跟癖好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.15,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}从明天起  我一定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.62,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不用再强颜欢笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:41.53,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}“只要坚信这一点  总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:44.51,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}会将心情完全传达…”这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:50.33,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}别逗了啦  难道不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.61,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我也已经不想再逃到什么地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:59.48,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}虽然有人说“yes！”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.49,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}可还是无法回到昨日的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:07.71,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}那是和你一起度过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:11.68,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}已经不想向任何人辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:16.01,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}所以说“yes！”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:20.03,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}因为任何人都已不再辩解  不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:24.47,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不是你的话就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:29.59,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}答案什么的  谁都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天就要结束了  天气还这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好晴朗  好晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时值晚春  午后又是如此的清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非要特意跑到百目鬼家来打麻将！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是在户外！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不行  难得那么好的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气的时候做出奇怪的举动会显得更奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说他除了动作以外其它地方也都很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴！听到没！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会打麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  你先来洗牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是搅和到一起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦  搅一搅就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  既然牌已码好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天胡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说起手的牌就能胡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果坐庄就是天胡  不坐庄就是地胡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态真好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像现在有\N赤木哲也和明菜在我背后一起守护一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}这里分别捏自三部麻将漫画「アカギ  ～闇に降り立った天才～」\N「哲也-雀聖と呼ばれた男」「スーパーヅガン」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接着来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿大车轮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}即胡牌由二筒到八筒的七副对子组成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清一色加宝牌八张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四喜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}即东南西北凑齐三副一将再加一副的胡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流局满贯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百目鬼  真老道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我难道还没怎样就输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是拿专用词汇评价你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「负班长」！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}「箱下」和「ぶっ飛び」都是得点为负的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.60,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,410)}平  胡{\fs16}\N\N{\fs18}此 花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日都已经下庄了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能再赢回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢什么啊  我不是说了我连麻将怎么打都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给四月一日你这个初学者一个恶补的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「麻将流浪传」？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「赌徒桃代」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「实录麻将一代记」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊  赌棍」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是什么乱七八糟的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓麻将  它就是人生  就是一场被称之为人生的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来体验一下让伟大的麻将好手们\N为之呕心沥血的赌博人生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「眼镜赌博地狱」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我看这种东西干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个挺不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「走运之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「背运之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你先把打法教给我好不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那里面不也有麻将入门嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  在四月一日学会之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先来打三人麻将吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:04:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有初学者在  就来一番缚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}即最少有一番才能胡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  这都哪跟哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说过不懂了  还非让我打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种做法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是在拿我寻开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在拿我寻开心吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？这个看上去不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雀Blaze·赌」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雀王Blaze自己中心流之最强麻将入门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲谈社出版！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是德语？…罗…特…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯…斯基？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就先一边看书一边看大家怎么打吧  写成四月一日的四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少挖苦我！你这黑馒头！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是明白点了  说白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓麻将牌  就是写有从一到九数字的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中又分为筒子  条子  万子三种字牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外  还有用汉字写成的字牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是东  南  西  北  白  发  中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好像在哪听到过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以三张相同花色数字相连的牌为一副
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以四副加一将为胡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（将：和牌牌形一般情况下是四个三张组，一个二张组，\N共十四张牌。这个二张组就是将牌（或雀头））
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡牌的方式遵循名为「役」的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不依此规则则不能胡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说  有一种名叫「断幺九」的役
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就规定要在没有数字一和九
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有字牌的情况下组成胡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要记住「一九不要  字牌不理」就好了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  侑子小姐  让我加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可不会让你们赢得那么轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还输得五体投地的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们几个会特意凑在一起打麻将？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么看都太古怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  该到四月一日了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我抓牌  慢的家伙会变成牛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一九不要  字牌不理…一九不要  字牌不理…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…完全行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（接下来）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸  别的没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的棘手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  其实也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是追上来点似乎就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  他是想早点坐庄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一把要看四月一日的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样  第一次打麻将的感受？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难死了  要什么不来什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要的倒一张一张地上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个游戏就是要你巧妙地换牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后码出高番的胡牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是这样没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直奔着断幺九的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边抓一边念着「一九不要  字牌不理」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是～可是～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是国士无双啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}国士无双  即十三幺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还真是什么都不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国士无双
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅由一九的数牌和字牌组成的役
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为麻将最强手  役满的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（miku…）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是臭手越穷琢磨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭手也有蒙中的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭手的思量和休息无异
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  形容得真是到位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别给我臭手臭手地说个没完！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都对我这初学者…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是来做什么  小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来还百目鬼同学借我的书的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击～你说啥～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  百目鬼那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然背着我和小葵玩借书…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  可以的话请收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上烹饪课的时候做多的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？还有蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樱桃塔尔特蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  小葵亲·手·做·的·蛋糕啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是朋友做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思呢  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学还会打麻将啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  其实今天是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…而且还是一窍不通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再扔了这个就叫听了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就赢了吗  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  好棒  好棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能叫这家伙得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清老头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}全部由三张一九条  万  筒组成的胡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑眯眯七对子带宝牌两张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}14张牌中有7组2张一样的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平胡二杯口加宝牌两张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}平胡，平胡即最基本的胡牌。\N二杯口，二色二顺，指所胡牌中有2个同色同数的两副顺子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日君同学好厉害  一败涂地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕我会好好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰碰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰碰碰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（接下来）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿  你可不要欺人太甚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再碰出中暗刻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（这里有些奇怪，因为暗刻只能自摸出来，明刻才是碰出来的）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就明摆着是大三元了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}胡牌中含有三组三元牌(中发白)的刻子或杠子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  也许它只是单纯喜欢凑齐同样花色的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰碰碰碰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑…侑子小姐  到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日  你已经让摩可拿铁定役满了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这牌胡了就是32000点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让摩可拿自摸了  这把可就要都算在四月一日一个人头上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（接下来）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡了  凑齐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿  振听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}摩可拿之前扔过一张自摸的能胡的一筒，所以现在它除非再自摸出\N一张一筒来否则是不能胡的，这种情况就属于振听的一种。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说这是不能胡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}因为这张一筒是摩可拿碰的，而不是自摸出来的，所以说不能胡。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来它好像没太在意的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要漂亮地凑齐牌码就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是四月一日帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他  看他还能惹什么笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（负责任）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  为什么突然要打麻将呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起打麻将来说  洗牌的过程更为重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  最后一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在惦记着逆转吗？  四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我说话  我现在正在思考呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（四月一日  绿一色  缺一张听）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（百目鬼  两天秤  三色  缺一张听）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（摩可拿  四暗刻  单骑  缺一张听）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（侑子  小四喜  四暗刻  听牌）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（听北  六筒）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着叫听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（听单骑一条）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也叫听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还准备玩一把老道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（听三六条）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是说…我已经站在了悬崖边上？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道四月一日那只手能抓出什么来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  别啰啰嗦嗦的  该你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听牌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你说得对  反正我是个初学者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我的意思是你说你还差一张就胡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  雨童女  你怎么会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然来了这张  那当然要打那张了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赖着不打的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成牛吧  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫听…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还空着一张  你听什么听！笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨童女  难得你远道而来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能不能不要宠我们家的四月一日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们家的」是什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这家伙太迟钝  就忍不住打下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  要是连这把都没胡你不觉得懊恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来你已经输了个底儿掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  还成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是座敷童子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是绿色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿一色    听牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全让你给说出去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那…那个  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是预料之外的发展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我们也叫听了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（绿一色  只由绿色的牌组成的胡牌  役满）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是摩可拿要的牌  就只能扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是北风或者六筒  我就胡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果上绿牌的话  毫无疑问那就只能让四月一日…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸一条  不要摸到绿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「赢了」个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把役满48000点的机会放跑了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那我应该是几点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人1000点  一共3000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说总是让妖怪附身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到了麻将上还是一样背运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结局还算不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日  负91700点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了就是输了  四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  我认输还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种漂亮的自爆真是百年难遇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起　我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　没你什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是这家伙自己倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧　你要怎么还赌债呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说　又要把打工时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要按我的利息算法　你得打工到下辈子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是脱衣麻将啊　Year～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人的灵魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很开心的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗麻将牌的声音是一种吉兆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对祈求安宁的人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一种向死者的饯别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去向该去的地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她笑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小羽也会高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴会？现在就开始！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  四月一日你以为你输了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回店里去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就想吃～现在就想喝～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  在这里！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏花啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又不是在陌生人家里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我厨房  百目鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我来帮忙好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那孩子帮起忙来越帮越乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿也去～摩可拿也去～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  要是赏花的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做点能吃的就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样拜托的工作就结束了  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  毕竟光靠我念的经是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  对她来说那也是件值得高兴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价是你爷爷秘藏的陈酒  拜托了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
